The evidence with the title 'Fact-checking Ted Cruz | PolitiFact ' says Oct 17, 2013  ... UPS left 15,000 employees ' spouses "without health insurance" and told them to, " go on an exchange with no employer subsidy." Cruz ignored the fact that the only spouses being kicked off the UPS plan would be the ones who already had access to an employer - sponsored plan in their own job. 
